title: Luxe. Rustic. Modern!
posting_body: ['Text ID # 2768C to my cell for more info!', 'Luxe.', 'Rustic.', 'Modern.1, 2 & 3 Bedroom Floor Plans Brushy Creek Come home to a space that is unapologetically you.', 'The farmhouse-style one, two, and three bedroom floor plans feature bright, welcoming finishes that exude rustic charm while perfectly complementing your decorative style.', "Your new home isn't just lovely to look at, either.", 'Each apartment comes equipped with smart home features that bring an added air of ease and convenience to your daily routine.', 'Thoughtfully designed kitchens come equipped with energy-efficient appliances – ideal for everything from hosting large gatherings to weekly meal prep.', 'Finally, your private balcony or patio extends your upscale living space and lets you enjoy the warm Texas sun while you sip on your morning cup of Joe.', 'From your one, two, or three bedroom farmhouse-style apartment to amenity-rich social spaces, we are a high-end, charming community created for comfort, style, and functionality.', 'Wake up in an active mood?', 'Meet your fitness goals on your schedule at the 24-hour fitness center, or go for a swim in a resort-style swimming pool.', 'Feel like staying in?', 'Let your apartment level up your home base with a gourmet-style kitchen outfitted with energy-efficient stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, and custom cabinetry.', 'Finally, catch up with neighbors at the clubhouse before taking the pup for some off-leash fun at the onsite dog park.', 'At The Avery, we provide the good life.', 'You live it.', "Inside and out, we deliver an elevated at-home experience that you'll wonder how you ever lived without."]
